<h3>The GreatSchools Network</h3>

<p>
    GreatSchools is committed to serving all parents, regardless of the economic, language or technological barriers
    they face. The <b><i>GreatSchools Network</i></b> engages a broad cross-section of parents by interacting with
    them
    directly in their schools and communities. The Network provides parents with access to workshops and printed
    materials, and brings together a community of parents, schools and partner organizations that share the
    GreatSchools
    vision of quality schools for all children. The Network is currently working with parents in San Francisco, CA
    and
    soon will be expanding to Dayton, Ohio, and Washington, D.C.</p>
